    <p>Wealth &amp; Asset Operations Track • Unit 31: Front-to-Back Operational Coordination</p>
    <h1 id="hero-title">Lesson 31.4: Escalation and Issue Handling</h1>
    <p>
      Study escalation protocols and resolution methods for operational and workflow issues — how problems are identified, classified, escalated to the appropriate authority level, investigated, resolved, and documented to prevent recurrence in front-to-back wealth and asset management operations.
    </p>
  </section>
